New to the list, just wanted to say hello to all. 



I have been doing some read and thinking, which the two put together can
really be dangerous.



I saw the person posted the scanner and radio frequencies, though I can seem
to find his email. 



I have thought about this very same idea and not being a radio person I
really have no clue.  But I wanted to also scan a given list of radio
frequencies that are not use in my area here in Philadelphia.  



So I ask  if anyone in the ITC and EVP world might have some insight or has
had any luck with specific radio frequencies that showed promise for ITC and
or evps?  



If you could share you radio frequencies and experiences  





Thanks!



